  18:Core/BSP/multi_button.c **** /**
  19:Core/BSP/multi_button.c ****   * @brief  Initialize the button struct handle
  20:Core/BSP/multi_button.c ****   * @param  handle: the button handle struct
  21:Core/BSP/multi_button.c ****   * @param  pin_level: read the HAL GPIO of the connected button level
  22:Core/BSP/multi_button.c ****   * @param  active_level: pressed GPIO level
  23:Core/BSP/multi_button.c ****   * @param  button_id: the button id
